sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as RHOAI Gateway / Istio<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant API as vLLM OpenAI API Server<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant Engine as AsyncLLM Engine (V1)<br/>PagedAttention
    participant Storage as Model Storage<br/>PVC / S3 / HF Hub

    Note over Client,Storage: Flow 1: OpenAI-Compatible Inference Request
    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Auth: Bearer Token / mTLS
    Gateway->>API: Forward HTTP/8000<br/>API Key (optional)
    API->>Engine: In-process / IPC call
    Engine->>Engine: PagedAttention + Continuous Batching
    Engine-->>API: Generated tokens (streaming)
    API-->>Gateway: HTTP SSE stream / JSON response
    Gateway-->>Client: HTTPS response

    Note over Client,Storage: Flow 2: gRPC Router Communication
    participant Router as Rust Router<br/>50051/TCP gRPC/HTTP2
    Router->>API: gRPC VllmEngine.Generate<br/>50051/TCP plaintext
    API->>Engine: In-process call
    Engine-->>API: Streaming tokens
    API-->>Router: gRPC streaming response

    Note over Client,Storage: Flow 3: Model Loading at Startup
    Engine->>Storage: HTTPS/443 - Download from HuggingFace Hub<br/>Auth: HF Token (optional)
    Storage-->>Engine: Model weights & tokenizer
    Engine->>Storage: HTTPS/443 - Load from S3<br/>Auth: AWS/S3 credentials
    Storage-->>Engine: Model artifacts
    Engine->>Storage: File I/O - Read from PVC
    Storage-->>Engine: Cached model weights
